# pb

This repository contains the source code of the web interface to the ‘Persönliche Bekanntschaften’ project [1] on Toolforge [2] and of the bot that transfers data from the German Wikipedia to the database on Labs. The project is about the confirmation of acquitances between users.

[1] https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Persönliche_Bekanntschaften
[2] https://pb.toolforge.org/

More information are available in Czech [3], Dutch [4], French [5], German [6].

[3] https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Osobn%C3%AD_zn%C3%A1mosti
[4] https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Ontmoete_Wikimedianen
[5] https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Connaissances_personnelles
[6] https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Persönliche_Bekanntschaften

## Requirements
  - Python 3:
     - PyMySQL: https://pypi.org/project/PyMySQL/
     - jinja2
  - MySQL
